{"tid":1177004,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"等錶位要唔要排隊","createTime":"2019-05-29T14:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T03:08:17.000Z","uid":189895,"like":216,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"e64dc7c339403f23c9ce4654e4cff51c4a18cbcc","tid":1177004,"uid":189895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:12:42.000Z","msg":"頭先路德圍食飯，去到等，唔使3分鐘咁啱有車走，喺正自己停個位，喺五、六個車位後個呀哥話佢黎排隊先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應唔應該讓<br />\n（附近無車等緊）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔讓係正確，我好彩楝中點解要讓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />排隊啦仆街"},{"pid":"2984604e9ac3ff6c1c96392fd0d22609e9741728","tid":1177004,"uid":76819,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:16:54.000Z","msg":"錶位從來都係邊個近邊個攞<br />\n除非好似赤柱沙灘嗰啲，你塞住個入口做條隊出嚟"},{"pid":"79a7a5aadb18571516f990339f1e067366a9da2b","tid":1177004,"uid":33004,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:24:18.000Z","msg":"好撚驚會俾人拉花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b00908d47427c402c292437e9423db45cad848e","tid":1177004,"uid":79410,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:30:28.000Z","msg":"邊個近就邊個泊架啦. <br />\n唔通你喺車場頭, 我喺車場尾有位入, 又俾你泊呀?<br />\n你話你架車同前面架車之間嗰個錶位架車走. 咁就邊個嚟就邊個泊先啫.<br />\n5,6個車位咁遠. 問佢係咪D 錶位佢等晒?"},{"pid":"bae225c7f61ccdee1fe1c5f547564b66a8ee27a7","tid":1177004,"uid":189895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b00908d47427c402c292437e9423db45cad848e","tid":1177004,"uid":79410,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:30:28.000Z","msg":"邊個近就邊個泊架啦. <br />\n唔通你喺車場頭, 我喺車場尾有位入, 又俾你泊呀?<br />\n你話你架車同前面架車之間嗰個錶位架車走. 咁就邊個嚟就邊個泊先啫.<br />\n5,6個車位咁遠. 問佢係咪D 錶位佢等晒?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:31:09.000Z","msg":"就係驚比人搞但我照泊"},{"pid":"35beccc9f24469f9bf4dabd3eb3cca1488c3347e","tid